<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.css">
    <script src="/js/jquery-1.11.3.min.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
    <script src="/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {padding-top: 50px; background: #eee;}
        .main {margin-top: 20px;  }
        .main .media-list {background: #fff; padding: 15px;}
        .main .media {border-bottom: 1px dotted #eee; padding-bottom: 20px;}
        .main .media-left img {width: 360px; height: 220px;}
        .hot li {line-height: 26px;}
        .hot li span {margin-right: 7px;}
        .footer {background: #101010; color: #9d9d9d; padding: 20px 0;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top navbar-inverse">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-header">
                <button class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#menu">
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                </button>
                <a href="" class="navbar-brand">牛的博客</a>
            </div>
            <div id="menu" class="collapse navbar-collapse">
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                    <li class="active"><a href="/">首页</a></li>
                    <% for (var i = 0; i < cats.length; i ++) { %>
                    <li><a href="/list?cat=<%= cats[i].title %>"><%= cats[i].title %></a></li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
                <form action="" class="navbar-form navbar-right">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control">
                        <div class="input-group-btn">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary">搜索</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <img src="images/baner.jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive">

    <div class="container main">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-9">
                <ul class="media-list">
                    <% for (var i = 0; i < posts.length; i++) {%>
                    <li class="media">
                        <a href="/post?id=<%= posts[i]._id %>" class="media-left">
                            <img src="<%= posts[i].cover %>" alt="">
                        </a>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h2><a href="/post?id=<%= posts[i]._id %>"><%= posts[i].subject %></a></h2>
                            <p>
                                <span><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>admin</span>
                                <span><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"><%= posts[i].time.toLocaleString() %></i></span>
                                <span><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-eye-open"><%= posts[i].count ? posts[i].count : 0  %>次浏览</i></span>
                                <a href=""> <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"></i>评论一下</a>
                            </p>
                            <p><%= posts[i].summary %></p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        热门文章
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body hot">
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li><span class="label label-danger">1</span><a href="">如何为网站和应用创建设计...</a></li>
                            <li><span class="label label-danger">2</span><a href="">如何为网站和应用创建设计...</a></li>
                            <li><span class="label label-danger">3</span><a href="">如何为网站和应用创建设计...</a></li>
                            <li><span class="label label-default">4</span><a href="">如何为网站和应用创建设计...</a></li>
                            <li><span class="label label-default">5</span><a href="">如何为网站和应用创建设计...</a></li>
                            <li><span class="label label-default">6</span><a href="">如何为网站和应用创建设计...</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer text-center">
        <p>版权所有，保留一切权利！ 转载内容版权归作者及来源网站所有，原创内容转载请注明来源。</p>
        <p>Copyright © 2013-2014 andy, All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
